## RelationType: 恢复任务明确时间点副本

恢复任务对象通过 timePointId 字段关联到时间点副本对象，明确恢复任务使用哪个时间点副本进行恢复。

### Endpoint

| Source | Target | Type |
|--------|--------|------|
| recovery_task | timepoint_copy | direct |

### Mapping Rules

| Source Property | Target Property |
|-----------------|-----------------|
| timePointId | timePointId |
